## 8. StoryGridCard Improvements

File: `client/src/components/StoryGridCard.tsx`

### Cover image aspect ratio
Enforce consistent 4:3 cover ratio so all cards have the same height:

```tsx
// Inside the card cover container:
sx={{
  width: "100%",
  aspectRatio: "4/3",
  overflow: "hidden",
  "& img": {
    width: "100%",
    height: "100%",
    objectFit: "cover",
    display: "block",
  },
}}
```

### Card hover state
Replace or supplement pure elevation lift with a warm border transition:

```tsx
<Card
  sx={{
    borderRadius: 3,
    border: "0.5px solid",
    borderColor: "divider",
    transition: "border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease",
    "&:hover": {
      borderColor: "primary.light",
      transform: "translateY(-3px)",
    },
    overflow: "hidden",
    height: "100%",
  }}
  elevation={0}
>
```

### Card body padding
Increase internal padding for breathing room:

```tsx
// Card body Box:
sx={{ p: 2.5 }}  // was likely p: 2
```

