## What NOT to Change

- Do not modify `fetchStoriesWithFilters` or any Firestore query logic
- Do not change the route structure or `useLangNavigate` usage
- Do not add text search to this page (search lives in SearchPage)
- Do not add server-side filtering (client-side useMemo is intentional)
- Do not change the 3-filter model (age / category / topic)
- Do not reuse `catalogVariant` prop on StoryGridCard here (it's used on other pages)
- Do not add a 4th grid column at any breakpoint
- Do not hide filters behind an accordion or modal

---

## Architecture Notes

- Route registered in `App.tsx` as `<Route path="books" element={<AllBooksPage />} />`
- Language-prefixed via `/:lang/*` parent route (e.g. `/he/books`, `/en/books`)
- `StoryGridCard` is shared across: `AgeResultsPage`, `CategoryResultsPage`, `TopicResultsPage`, `SearchPage`, `FavoritesPage`, `RelatedStories`
- Changes to `StoryGridCard` affect ALL of the above pages — test across them
- `AGE_GROUPS` imported from `../components/MegaMenu/data` — do not duplicate
- Category/topic dropdown options are derived from loaded stories, not from `useReferenceData`
